name: Vegelbud Labyrinth
description:
This is my last game. I was on this project for about 3 months. I learned a lot from previous game, but from this too. This game is meant for playing and enjoying it. It has some fun features, like endless, random generated map. It has only 3 self-made map.

I can't attach the source code here, because this was my thesis at uni. From around 2020 summer, it will be available at edit.elte.hu.
